{"tid":2229936,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解人愈大愈難喊？","createTime":"2020-10-04T16:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T09:44:23.000Z","uid":56639,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c2c4585c242438b4e6a44bad8e05162214f678","tid":2229936,"uid":56639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"以前細個唔開心個陣<br />\n可以大喊一場<br />\n喊完就無事 好似釋放哂所有嘢咁<br />\n<br />\n但係點解大個左<br />\n遇到傷心嘅事<br />\n最多只會眼濕濕 流幾滴眼淚<br />\n有時心痛到成個人震哂都喊唔到<br />\n欲哭無淚嘅感覺好難受<br />\n<br />\n係因為人愈大 遇到傷心嘅事愈嚟愈多？已經開始無感覺？<br />\n<br />\n定因為人愈大 愈嚟愈堅強 唔會再好似以前咁輕易流淚？<br />\n<br />\n好想大喊一場就無事<br />\n唔想每日個心都有野哽住 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831d58f5b785025351ba148fda20720ca8f871c1","tid":2229936,"uid":229353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"喊緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b4696678c75a136907c4f6d80078962267e438","tid":2229936,"uid":204466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"揾人傾下"},{"pid":"4ee7ca21f527de9b556ff201dd9a1a70f81f4efb","tid":2229936,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"愈大愈易喊<br />\n但唔係因為唔開心喊"},{"pid":"c2cb87cf387746be8602bfe96b5b7c02012b0eb3","tid":2229936,"uid":369296,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"我可以分享一首歌俾你聽，包保你喊，不過都係算啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edbbf34b7f469487c6937374e6111992594cdc3","tid":2229936,"uid":378305,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"你有男友、將你初菊既第一次比左佢、就會痛到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"